          ski behind for a high-speed, adrenaline-racing adventure!  The 24-foot Leisure Kraft 
          has room for 10 people, an awning and a 115 hp, 4-stroke engine.<br><br>
      </td>
    </tr> 
    <tr>
      <td>
        <img src="/assets/dbldeckerpontoon.jpg" alt="Nickajack Marina Double Decker Pontoon Boats" width="250" class="pull-left">
